### ===========================
### Admin Ticket Management
### ===========================

### List tickets (default)
# Fetches the first page of tickets with default sorting (newest first).
GET {{host}}/api/admin/tickets
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List tickets (paginated)
# Fetches the second page of tickets with a page size of 10.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/tickets?page=1&size=10
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List tickets (filter by status)
# Fetches only tickets with OPEN status.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/tickets?status=OPEN
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List tickets (filter by priority)
# Fetches only URGENT priority tickets.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/tickets?priority=URGENT
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List tickets (filter by category)
# Fetches only tickets in the PAYMENT_PROBLEM category.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/tickets?category=PAYMENT_PROBLEM
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List tickets (filter by assignee)
# Fetches tickets assigned to a specific support member.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/tickets?assigneeId={{support_user_id}}
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List tickets (search by subject)
# Searches tickets whose subject contains the given query.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/tickets?search=payment
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List tickets (sorted by priority descending)
# Fetches tickets sorted by priority (most urgent first).
GET {{host}}/api/admin/tickets?sort=priority&direction=DESC
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List tickets (sorted by last message)
# Fetches tickets sorted by most recent message activity.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/tickets?sort=lastMessageAt&direction=DESC
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List tickets (combined filters)
# Searches for open high-priority payment problems, sorted by creation date.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/tickets?status=OPEN&priority=HIGH&category=PAYMENT_PROBLEM&sort=createdAt&direction=DESC&page=0&size=20
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Get ticket detail
# Fetches detailed information about a specific ticket including its full conversation history.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/tickets/{{ticket_id}}
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Update ticket (change status)
# Transitions a ticket to IN_PROGRESS status.
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/tickets/{{ticket_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### Update ticket (change priority)
# Escalates a ticket to URGENT priority.
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/tickets/{{ticket_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "priority": "URGENT"
}

### Update ticket (assign)
# Assigns a ticket to a support team member.
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/tickets/{{ticket_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "assigneeUserId": "{{support_user_id}}"
}

### Update ticket (multiple fields)
# Updates status, priority, and assigns a ticket in one request.
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/tickets/{{ticket_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "assigneeUserId": "{{support_user_id}}"
}

### Update ticket (resolve)
# Resolves a ticket.
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/tickets/{{ticket_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "status": "RESOLVED"
}

### Update ticket (close)
# Closes a ticket permanently.
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/tickets/{{ticket_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "status": "CLOSED"
}

### Reply to ticket as support
# Adds a support reply to a ticket. Automatically transitions IN_PROGRESS/OPEN tickets to AWAITING_USER.
POST {{host}}/api/admin/tickets/{{ticket_id}}/reply
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "body": "Thank you for reaching out. We've reviewed your issue and here's what we found:\n\n1. Your payment was processed successfully.\n2. The confirmation may take up to 30 minutes to appear.\n\nPlease let us know if you have any further questions."
}

### Get ticket statistics
# Returns dashboard statistics: open tickets, in-progress, awaiting user, resolved today, and average resolution time.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/tickets/stats
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
